main event: A civilian observed a round object that appeared as a red glare, similar to a light bulb, hovering 20 miles northwest of Minneapolis.
interesting points: The object seemed to hover in place, The sighting occurred on July 25, 1955, at 0145Z GMT, The observer reported the object looked like a light bulb, There is insufficient data for evaluation of the object, The report indicates uncertainty about the nature of the object.
sighted object: a round object with a red glare
